ARM: dts: gose: enable sound DMA support in device tree

Enable DMA transfer to/from SSI in r8a7793/gose device tree.

     DMA
[MEM] -> [SSI]

     DMA
[MEM] <- [SSI]

Based on similar work for the r8a7791/koelsch by Kuninori Morimoto.

